 To propose to a girl, a man must possess a romantic gesture which communicates his intent. Typically, romantic gestures are not inexpensive, thus a man must produce such a gesture with some level of financial constraint. A man who is fully capable of providing for the girl will, without fail, be able to make a romantic gesture. However, if a man cannot provide for the girl, then he will have to resort to cheaper romantic gestures, and other means of communication. The man must communicate his intent
